CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.sdoh_cdc_wonder_natality.county_natality`
(
  Year DATE OPTIONS(description="Year"),
  County_of_Residence STRING OPTIONS(description="County of Residence"),
  County_of_Residence_FIPS STRING OPTIONS(description="County of Residence Code"),
  Births INT64 OPTIONS(description="Number of Births"),
  Ave_Age_of_Mother FLOAT64 OPTIONS(description="Average Age of Mother (years)"),
  Ave_OE_Gestational_Age_Wks FLOAT64 OPTIONS(description="Average OE Gestational Age (weeks)"),
  Ave_LMP_Gestational_Age_Wks FLOAT64 OPTIONS(description="Average LMP Gestational Age (weeks)"),
  Ave_Birth_Weight_gms FLOAT64 OPTIONS(description="Average Birth Weight (grams)"),
  Ave_Pre_pregnancy_BMI FLOAT64 OPTIONS(description="Average Pre-pregnancy BMI"),
  Ave_Number_of_Prenatal_Wks FLOAT64 OPTIONS(description="Average Number of Prenatal Visits")
)
OPTIONS(
  labels=[("freebqcovid", "")]
);
